@page "/"

<PageTitle>eSkolar</PageTitle>

<!-- HERO SECTION -->
<section class="hero-section" id="home">
    <!-- Logo -->
    <div class="hero-logo">
        <img src="/images/main/eskolar_logo.png" alt="eSkolar Logo" />
    </div>
    
    <!-- Title, subtitle, and CTA -->
    <div class="hero-content">
        <h1 class="hero-title">
            Empowering Students.<br>
            Connecting Opportunities.
        </h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">
            Your One-Stop Hub for Scholarships and Academic Opportunities
        </p>
        <div class="hero-buttons">
            <NavLink href="/signup" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Get Started</NavLink>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- FEATURES SECTION -->
<section class="features-section" id="about">
    <!-- What is eSkolar -->
    <div class="container1">
        <h3 class="section-title">What is eSkolar?</h3>
        <div class="features-grid">
            <div class="feature-card1">
                <p>eSkolar combines the word “scholar” with the prefix “e-” which stands for electronic or digital. This name reflects the system’s goal of bringing scholarship-related services into one digital platform. It also honors the “Iskolar ng Bayan” identity of PUP students, updating it for the digital age while keeping its connection to the community and tradition.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Why Choose eSkolar -->
    <div class="container2">
        <h3 class="section-title">Why Choose eSkolar?</h3>
        <div class="features-grid">

            <!-- For students -->
            <div class="feature-card2">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <img src="/images/main/students.svg" alt="Students" class="icon-svg" />
                </div>
                <p>For <strong>students</strong> seeking academic opportunities, eSkolar provides a centralized platform to discover, track, and manage scholarship applications.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- For institutions -->
            <div class="feature-card2">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <img src="/images/main/institutions.svg" alt="Students" class="icon-svg" />
                </div>
                <p>For school and institution <strong>administrators</strong>, eSkolar streamlines the management of scholars and scholarship programs.</p>
            </div>
            
             <!-- For benefactors -->
            <div class="feature-card2">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <img src="/images/main/benefactors.svg" alt="Students" class="icon-svg" />
                </div>
                <p>For <strong>benefactors</strong> such as companies, foundations, and organizations, eSkolar provides tools to post opportunities, review and monitor scholar outcomes, and gain insights through analytics.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>